<h1>Getting Started</h1>

Getting started with Docular is as simple as adding the grunt-docular Grunt plugin to your project and then simply start creating your documentation.

The grunt-docular plugin provides the tool that compiles your documentation and generates resources for the webapp for viewing.

The documentation syntax is best learned through examples that are provided here and in other portions of the Docular documentation.

<h2>Installation Steps</h2>

